         <h1>FAQs</h1>
          <div class="faq"><a name="Why"></a>
          <h3>Why take out a subscription? <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>With a subscription you can look forward to receiving your favourite magazine through your door every month, saving you the time and trouble of going to the shops to buy a copy. If you take advantage of one of our special discount offers a subscription will also save you money compared to the normal magazine cover price. Don't forget subscriptions also make a great gift (see <a href="#Gift">gift subscriptions</a>).</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="How"></a>
          <h3>How can I order a subscription online? <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>Choose a magazine from the magazine home page. Click on the button next to the appropriate subscription offer and click 'Add to basket'. You will then be able to view your 'Shopping Basket'. If you would like to order any further magazine subscriptions please click 'Continue shopping'. Once you have finished shopping simply click 'Checkout', where you will be asked to fill out your delivery details and method of payment.</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="Confirmation"></a>
          <h3>How will my subscription be confirmed? <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>You will receive an email confirmation of your order within 24 hours.</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="First"></a>
          <h3>When will the first issue of my subscription be dispatched? <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>After your order has been processed, your confirmation letter will be sent and this will include details about when your first magazine will be sent to you.</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="Sign"></a>
          <h3>Do I have to sign for my magazine each time it is delivered? <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>No, your magazine will be sent through the normal post.</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="Renew"></a>
          <h3>How do I renew my subscription? <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>You can renew your subscription online at any time. Simply login to your account. If you choose not to renew online you will receive notification of the need to renew your subscription in enough time to ensure you don't miss any issues of your magazine.</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="Address"></a>
          <h3>How do I notify you about a change of address? <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>If you have changed your address during your subscription period you can amend your details online by login into your account. Please note, if you are relocating to another country then please contact us on the number above and we will be happy to assist.</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="Gift"></a>
          <h3>Gift subscriptions <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>Magazine subscriptions make the ideal gift for just about anybody. To give a subscription as a gift simply go to the individual magazine page and choose 'Someone else' to the question 'Who are you buying for?'. When we send you the written confirmation we will include a gift card for you to send to the gift recipient so that you can add your personal touch and retain the element of surprise. You will also be given the choice to send your e-card electronically to your chosen recipient.</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="Price"></a>
          <h3>What is included in the price? <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>Prices displayed include delivery costs and taxes (where applicable). Any discounts to the normal issue cover price will also be explained. If you pay for your subscription using any non-sterling currency the price you pay will be dependent on the exchange rate of your credit card company and may fluctuate.</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="DD"></a>
          <h3>Direct Debits <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>UK customers have the option to subscribe by direct debit. Depending on the magazine, your payments will be spread into easy, manageable 3, 6 or 12 monthly payments. As direct debit is a continuous payment method you are in complete control of your subscription as well as eliminating the need for renewal notices.</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="Secure"></a>
          <h3>Is the online payment system secure? <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>Yes. We use SSL encryption software to keep the details of your order and credit/debit card information secure.</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="Overseas"></a>
          <h3>Can I order a subscription for delivery to an address outside the UK? <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>Yes. As the magazines are despatched from the UK, higher delivery costs may apply for delivery to addresses outside the UK. These will be displayed in the price summary once you have selected the country to which you want the magazines delivered. The prices displayed include delivery costs and taxes (where applicable).</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="Late"></a>
          <h3>What can I do if I do not receive an issue on time? <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>Please email our customer services team or contact them using the information above. Remember to include your subscriber reference number or full mailing address.  Please remember to notify our customer services team if you change address.<br> UK Customers can access the latest information about delivery service disruption in their local area at <a href="http://www.royalmail.com/serviceupdates">www.royalmail.com/serviceupdates</a></p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq"><a name="NoGift"></a>
          <h3>I haven't received my free gift? <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"><!----></span></h3>
          <div class="toggle">
          <p>If your subscription offer entitled you to a free gift, please note this is sent separately to the acknowledgment letter and can take up to 28 days to arrive. Should you not receive your gift within 28 days please contact our helpful <a href="/contact-us">customer services team</a>.</p>
          </div>
          </div>
          <p>If you have a question which has not been answered here, please email our <a href="mailto:sewinspired@servicehelpline.co.uk">customer services team</a> remembering to include your subscriber reference number or full mailing address.</p>

          </div>
